<br/>
project 'hello' built successfully<br/>
<br/>
C:\soul-5.0.0\tools\otava\test\hello><br/>
            </div>
        </li>
        This builds the hello world application for the <span class="mono">debug</span> configuration.
    </ul>
</p>
<p>
    Testing:
    <ul>
        <li>
            Then execute the application by entering command <span class="mono">bin\debug\hello</span>:
            <div class="console">
C:\soul-5.0.0\tools\otava\test\hello>bin\debug\hello<br/>
Hello, world!<br/>
<br/>
C:\soul-5.0.0\tools\otava\test\hello><br/>
            </div>
        </li>
    </ul>
</p>
